{"date":"2010-05-18","platform":"全部游戏","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/73/23/3504_Q97Xc.jpg"},"summary":"《荒野大镖客：救赎》（英语：Red Dead Redemption，台港译作“碧血狂杀”）是一款开放世界的西部动作冒险游戏，由Rockstar San Diego开发，Rockstar Games发行。2010年5月18日在PlayStation 3和Xbox 360上发行。它是2004年《红色死亡左轮》的精神继承者。\r\n\r\n游戏的大部分故事发生在1911年，美国旧西部解体之后。游戏的主角John Marston从前是个罪犯，他出发去寻找从前的帮派同伙。Marston的妻儿被政府扣作人质，以迫使他成为一名赏金猎人。Marston别无选择，只能去寻找三名从前的同伴以让他们受到法律的制裁。\r\n\r\n发售之后，该游戏在Metacritic和GameRankings上均得到高分，使得它成为PlayStation 3和Xbox 360平台上最受好评的游戏之一。它的画面、音乐、开放世界的系统、剧情均得到评论家好评。据NPD Sales Group统计，该游戏仅在当年五六月份便卖出200万份。\r\n\r\nsource:https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%92%E9%87%8E%E5%A4%A7%E9%95%96%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%9A%E6%95%91%E8%B5%8E","name":"Red Dead Redemption","name_cn":"荒野大镖客：救赎","tags":[{"name":"Rockstar","count":37},{"name":"PS3","count":29},{"name":"ACT","count":19},{"name":"XBOX360","count":19},{"name":"R星","count":16},{"name":"西部沙箱","count":13},{"name":"荒野大镖客：救赎","count":13},{"name":"荒野大镖客","count":9},{"name":"2010","count":6},{"name":"XboxOne","count":5},{"name":"西部","count":4},{"name":"TPS","count":4},{"name":"射击感差","count":2},{"name":"弱智AI","count":2},{"name":"视频通关","count":1},{"name":"开放世界","count":1},{"name":"8分","count":1},{"name":"时代の挽歌","count":1},{"name":"16-20","count":1},{"name":"Rockstar_Games","count":1},{"name":"枪械科普好游戏","count":1},{"name":"三公主","count":1},{"name":"沙盒游戏","count":1},{"name":"87","count":1},{"name":"Open-World","count":1},{"name":"美国","count":1},{"name":"神作","count":1},{"name":"2012","count":1},{"name":"重复","count":1},{"name":"历史","count":1}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"荒野大镖客：救赎"},{"key":"平台","value":[{"v":"Xbox 360"},{"v":"PS3"}]},{"key":"游戏类型","value":"动作冒险"},{"key":"游戏引擎","value":"RAGE"},{"key":"游